⚾️ New Contest Alert ⚾️ Win a Chance to win tickets to a Cubs game or a once in a lifetime ultimate Cubs experience ❗️
I’m collaborating with @pepsi X Cubs for the #FlyYourFandomContest, Here are the steps to enter : 
1) Use a 20oz Pepsi bottle as your mic and sing “ Take me out to the ball game “ 
2) WEAR YOUR CUBS GEAR⚾️😁
3) Tag @pepsi , make sure logo shows🥤
Remember it’s not about your singing , HAVE FUN !

⚾️ New Contest Alert ⚾️ Win a Chance to win tickets to a Cubs game or a once in a lifetime ultimate Cubs experience ❗️
I’m collaborating with @pepsi X Cubs for the #FlyYourFandomContest, Here are the steps to enter : 
1) Use a 20oz Pepsi bottle as your mic and sing “ Take me out to the ball game “ 
2) WEAR YOUR CUBS GEAR⚾️😁
3) Tag @pepsi , make sure logo shows🥤
Remember it’s not about your singing , HAVE FUN !
